Label: Person name part 4: key name(s)
Description: The fourth part of a structured name of a person who contributed to the creation of the product: key name(s), ie the name elements normally used to open an entry in an alphabetical list, eg ‘Smith’ or ‘Garcia Marquez’ or ‘Madonna’ or ‘Francis de Sales’ (in Saint Francis de Sales). Non-repeating. Required if name part elements P.7.11 to P.7.18 are used.
Format: <dd>Variable length text, suggested maximum length 100 characters</dd>
